examples.en: The upbeat music matched her mood.
His strength is matched by his intelligence.
The teams are pretty equally matched.
She matched her wits against his strength.
The two teams are very evenly matched.
Her skirt and sweater matched perfectly.
They matched their best horse against my poor Dopey in a race.
Agassi was matched against Sampras in the final.
The company matched the discount policy of its competitors.
The drapery for the picture window matched the color of the furniture in the center of the room.
